snippet: The Secret Service has reassigned agents from its special operations division, including the top agent there, after a pair of embarrassing incidents earlier this year....

headline.print_headline: Secret Service Agents Reassigned After Incidents
headline.main: Secret Service Agents Reassigned After Incidents

lead_paragraph: The Secret Service has reassigned agents from its special operations division, including the top agent there, after a pair of embarrassing incidents earlier this year.
